FBIS3-36909 "drsov028_b_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-028 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Feb 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Media Issues Radio, TV Programs Blacked Out Nationwide Ivanovo LD1002053094 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0500 GMT 10 Feb 94 LD1002053094 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Immediately after the morning news bulletin, transmission of Russian Television ceased in Ivanovo. The transmission of Ostankino First Channel Television, St. Petersburg TV, and Mayak, Yunost, and Radio Odin radio stations were also stopped. On all three TV channels Ivanovo people will only be able to view evening news bulletins. Local TV programs will be transmitted without change since the Ivanovo TV and radio company has no debt to the communications workers, our correspondent in that town, Oleg Alalykin, reports.
